ent pour changer l'ambiance de vos lectures.\nUtilisez les contr\u00f4les Oculus Quest pour zoomer et \u00eatre au plus pr\u00e8s des planches dessin\u00e9es.", "short_description": "Izneo est un service cross-plateformes permettant de lire des Mangas, BD, Webtoons et Comics.\nPour utiliser l'application vous devez poss\u00e9der un compte izneo (\u00e0 cr\u00e9er sur www.izneo.com).\nConnectez-vous \u00e0 votre compte et retrouvez vos albums \u00e0 lire en r\u00e9alit\u00e9 virtuelle dans des environnements configurables."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "1080x360_bg.png", "id": "1205263993211836", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982727_1205263996545169_9148883512724487229_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3RyFRwlPRpgQ7kNvgGxF3yj&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDILDaFuvN7ycRc9FMFgC0liJGEo-MgaDOiWM5OfkOK_Q&oe=67066774"}, {"file_name": "512.png", "id": "1050334919080944", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984471_1050334922414277_3741888985697961122_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=N6SG5K2bdmcQ7kNvgHM4y-F&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAepqJkcuWr3rYUoKjf95bXQTIetfF6UGN4u8TqtO2J3A&oe=670668D6"}, {"file_name": "2560x1440_bg.png", "id": "715429989842664", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982580_715429993175997_4462372464006952430_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5IItR36j7qwQ7kNvgEcBqTS&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBm1PaUqEkFkZQuuqpE6l-iIgs4dz9uTV6_kzLsPjYd_A&oe=67067DF7"}, {"file_name": "3000x900_pdp-art-safezone.png", "id": "629709414781356", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974472_629709421448022_713197402145434487_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=P3dXSl1j3uwQ7kNvgELCvwF&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com